### Reset Password API Test Requests

### 1. Test Email Sending (Development only)
POST {{host}}/api/auth/test-email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

### 2. Send OTP (Forgot Password)
POST {{host}}/api/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

### 3. Debug - Check OTPs for email (Development only)
GET {{host}}/api/auth/debug-otps/test@example.com

### 4. Verify OTP
POST {{host}}/api/auth/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "otp": "123456"
}

### 5. Reset Password
POST {{host}}/api/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "otp": "123456",
  "newPassword": "NewPassword123!",
  "confirmPassword": "NewPassword123!"
}

### Variables
@host = https://localhost:5001